AST Visitor that defines all the (Famix) entities of interest Famix entities are stored in a Map along with the IBindings to which they correspond

    • pushInitBlockMethod

      protected void pushInitBlockMethod(Method fmx)
      Special method InitBlock may be "created" in various steps, mainly when attributes are declared+initialized with the result of a method call.
      In such a case, we need to recover the previous metric values to add to them
